Society.Lands:
Topaz dragons were most often found in the [[Elemental Plane of Water]]., and they only made short visits to the [[Prime Material Plane]].

In the [[Unapproachable East]], topaz dragons could be found around the coastal regions of [[Aglarond]].<ref>

Topazes were among the different kinds of dragon known to lair near the [[Smokeholes]] for their warmth, at least temporarily while travelling over the [[High Ice]].{{ Cite book/Elminster's Ecologies/Anauroch|20}}

document_data.Notable Topaz Dragons:
* [[Tithonnas]], a thane of the gem dragon deity [[Sardior]], the Ruby Dragon.{{Cite web/The Legend of Sardior}}
* [[Kisonraathiisar]], the Wyrmking, the topaz wyrm ruler of the city of [[Westgate]] on the [[Dragon Coast]] until {{Yearlink|-349}}.<ref><ref>
* [[Iltharagh]], called Golden Night, a very old topaz dragon turned [[dracolich]] in the [[Cult of the Dragon]], who laired north of [[Luskan]].<ref><ref>
* [[Gaulauntyr]], called Glorytongue and the Thief Dragon, a mature adult who moved from near [[Waterdeep]] to a manor southeast of [[Arrabar]].<ref>{{Cite dragon/240/Wyrms of the North: Gaulauntyr|78}}<ref>{{Cite web/Wyrms of the North/Gaulauntyr, "Glorytongue"}}<ref>{{Cite web enhancement/Roll Call of Dragons}}{{Gaulauntyr race}}
* [[Kraxx]], a mature adult dwelling on the [[Wild Coast]] of [[Chult]].
